{{Infobox attraction | name = ''Cinematic'' | logo = Parque_Warner_Cinematic_logo.jpg | logo_width = 250px | image = | imagedimensions = | caption = | location = Parque Warner Madrid | section = [[Movie World Studios]] | status = Operating | opened = {{start date and age|July 1, 2015}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.europapress.es/chance/tendencias/noticia-julio-comienza-magia-parque-warner-madrid-20150630160246.html|title=On July 1 Magic Begins at Parque Warner in Madrid|work=Europa Press|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181108192738/https://www.europapress.es/chance/tendencias/noticia-julio-comienza-magia-parque-warner-madrid-20150630160246.html|archivedate=November 8, 2018|df=mdy-all}}</ref> <!--GENERAL STATISTICS--> | music = Hollywood Film Music Orchestra | duration = 15-20 minutes<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.europapress.es/turismo/destino-espana/turismo-urbano/noticia-parque-warner-cinematic-nuevo-espectaculo-parque-warner-20150720120217.html|title=Warner Cinematic Park, the new Warner Park show|publisher=Europe Press|date=2015-07-20|access-date=2018-11-08}}</ref> }}
'''''Cinematic''''' is a nighttime show at [[Parque Warner Madrid]], that features [[fireworks]], characters, live actors, water effects, [[pyrotechnics]], lasers, music, searchlights, decorated boat floats, and mist screen projections. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.parquewarner.com/en/node/20315|title=This has been our 2015 season}}</ref> ==Synopsis== ''Cinematic'' transpires on the waters of the Warner Bros. Studios lake at [[Parque Warner Madrid]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.parquewarner.com/en/node/22188|title=Cinematic in Warner Park ... Action!}}</ref>
The show begins with an announcer welcoming the guests, as he speaks jets of water shoot up in the center of the lake and a projection of the park logo appears on the wall of water. The music of the ''Hollywood Film Music Orchestra'' swells as the water changes from purple to red and all of the water jets are shooting in every which way. Just then scenes from iconic [[Warner Bros.]] films such as [[Free Willy]], and [[Speed Racer (film)|Speed Racer]] play out on the massive wall of water. The water shoots higher and continuously changes colors, until more projections appear of films such as [[Man of Steel (film)|Man of Steel]], [[The Great Gatsby (2013 film)|The Great Gatsby]], and [[Beetlejuice]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pa-community.com/parques/parque-warner/espectaculos/hollywood-fantasy|title=Warner Cinematic|publisher=PA Community}}</ref>
